headline: Kinder Morgan: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: HOUSTON (AP) — Kinder Morgan Inc. KMI) on Wednesday reported third-quarter net income of $628 million. On a per-share basis, the Houston-based company said it had net income of 28 cents.

headline: Kinder Morgan Reports Third Quarter 2025 Financial Results
summary: HOUSTON, October 22, 2025--KMI board of directors today approved a cash dividend of $0.2925 per share for the third quarter ($1.17 annualized), payable on November 17, 2025.
